    This partial contains a sidebar which can shrint to an iconbar. On medium and large screens
    it is possible to toggle between a sidebar and iconbar. On small screens the toggling reveals or hides 
    the iconbar only. The functionality remains the same.

    Useage: The partial must be positioned inside a <div class="wrapper"> and the content must be 
    positioned inside a <div class="content"> as such:
        
    <div class=wrapper>
        {{> _sidebar }}
        <div class="content">
            <p>here goes all content</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    The sidebar is activated by any button containing the id="sidebarCollapse"

    Source: https://bootstrapious.com/p/bootstrap-sidebar 
--}}

